::Aerotaur::
       He nods.  They're after Nightlight and little Trinity.  I can't 
remember what we did to them but they've bound themselves together out of a 
hatred of us."  He sighs.  "Do you think they'd notice if we tunneled through 
the mountain to the other side?"

--part1_16a.80f8138.298b03f6_boundary
